Changelog
======================
- `v. 0.1.2`

  - reshaped gui
  - night mode
  - scan on/off mode
  - debug mode
  - "removing clients" feature
  - scrollable area
  - more friendly sound
  - config files in user home directory

- `v. 0.1.0 - 0.1.1`

  - gui with limited rows number
  - deauth feature
  
